<h2>Welcome to Pact, <%= @user.first_name %>!</h2>

<p>We're Alex and Keri Spencer, the founders of Pact — and we wanted to personally welcome you.</p>

<p>We built Pact because we saw a problem that frustrated us: small businesses and independent professionals were being forced to choose between overpriced enterprise tools and clunky free alternatives just to get a document signed. That didn't sit right with us.</p>

<p>We believe that every freelancer, consultant, and small team deserves access to the same professional tools that big companies take for granted — without the big company price tag. That's why we built Pact to be simple, affordable, and genuinely useful from day one.</p>

<div class="highlight">
  <p><strong>Here's what you can do right now:</strong></p>
  <p>Upload a PDF, place signature fields, and send it for signing — your recipient doesn't even need an account. You'll also find a built-in contact manager to keep your clients organized with notes, tags, and activity tracking.</p>
</div>

<p>Your 14-day trial gives you full access to everything. Take your time, explore the app, and send a few documents. If it's not for you, cancel anytime — no hard feelings, no hoops to jump through.</p>

<p>If you have any questions, ideas, or just want to say hello — reply directly to this email. It comes straight to us, and we read every message.</p>

<p>Thanks for giving Pact a shot. We're glad you're here.</p>

<p>
  <strong>Alex & Keri Spencer</strong><br>
  <span class="meta-text">Founders, Pact</span>
</p>

